data.description: Fall in love with this perfect opportunity to get back to nature and relax by the serene shores of a beautiful lake. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathrooms, home boasts over 2,300 sqft of spacious living space, creating a haven for you and your loved ones. Home features enhanced security with a metal front gate, enjoy the warmth and ambiance of three inviting fireplaces, curb appeal: showcasing the timeless charm of stone bricks, creating a captivating front view that stands out in the neighborhood. Call your favorite realtor today.
